I'm Web Developer
Engr Ajman khan

  • Engr Ajman Khan is a web developer who is passionate about creating beautiful and functional websites.
  • He is skilled in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React.
  • He is always looking for new ways to improve his skills and learn new technologies.
Learn more

About Me

Engr Ajman Khan is a professional web developer who is passionate about creating beautiful and functional websites.

Developing With a Passion While Exploring The World.

Exploring the world can help you to grow as a developer and as a person. It can also help you to find new inspiration for your work.When you combine your passion for development with your love of travel, you can create amazing things that can impact people all over the world.

Developing with a passion is about more than just creating code. It's about using your skills to make a difference in the world.

Contact Me

We are a team of experienced web developers who specialize in building WooCommerce websites.

We offer a variety of services, including website design, development, and maintenance.

What Services I'm Providing

I am passionate about creating beautiful and functional websites that meet the needs of my clients.

UI/UX Design

I am a UI/UX designer who can help you create beautiful, intuitive, and user-friendly interfaces for your website, mobile app, or software product.I understand the importance of user experience and I work with you to create designs that meet the needs of your users and your business goals.

I use a variety of methods, including user research, wireframing, prototyping, and user testing to ensure that my designs are effective and usable.

Digital Marketing

I am a digital marketing specialist who can help you reach your target audience and grow your business online.

I offer a variety of services, including SEO, PPC, social media marketing, and content marketing.

I work with you to create a custom digital marketing plan that meets your specific needs and budget.

Web Development

I am a web designer who can help you create a beautiful, professional, and user-friendly website that meets your business needs.I use a variety of tools and techniques to create websites that are both visually appealing and functional.I work with you to understand your needs and goals, and then I create a website that is tailored to your specific requirements

Working Process

I am always working on new projects and learning new technologies.

I am excited to share my work in progress with potential clients and employers.

Work Experience

Here is my experienced.

UI/UX Designer 2022-2023

I have 3 years of experience in UI/UX design, with a focus on web and mobile applications.The companies where I have worked, such as  BilalGroup, Fiverr,Chegg and Upwork. 

UI/UX Designer Web Designer 2021-2023

I have worked with a variety of technologies, including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and Node.js.The companies where I have worked, such as  BilalGroup, Fiverr, and Upwork. 

Web Designer Database Administrator August 2022-Active

I am an active database administrator at Sarmaya PVT Ltd, with experience in MySQL, PostgreSQL,MongoDB,MS Server and Oracle.

Database Administrator FullStack developer August 2022-Active Remote job

I am an active remote full-stack developer at BilalGroup PVT Ltd, with experience in frontend and backend development.I am  responsible for the design, development, and deployment of BilalGroup's web and mobile applications.

Fullstack developer SEO and Digital marketing 2022-2023

I am a digital marketing specialist who can help you reach your target audience and grow your business online.I offer a variety of services, including SEO, PPC, social media marketing, and content marketing. BilalGroup, where I have worked .

About Me

Designing With Passion While Exploring The World

I am a passionate designer who loves to create beautiful and functional designs.I am also an avid traveler who loves to explore new cultures and meet new people.I believe that design and travel can be combined to create amazing experiences.

I also believe that travel is about more than just seeing new places. It's about learning about different cultures and meeting new people.

Let's talk with me.
ajman41288@gmail.com
I Create Products Not Just Arts

I believe that products should be more than just objects to use. They should also be works of art that people can enjoy.

I am passionate about product design because I believe that it has the power to make a positive impact on the world.

Frontend and Backend Developer
  • Frontend developers are responsible for the look and feel of a website. They use HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create the website's user interface (UI). This includes the website's layout, design, and interactivity. Frontend developers also work with frontend frameworks and libraries to speed up development and make it easier to create complex UIs.
  • Backend developers are responsible for the functionality of a website. They use server-side programming languages like Java, Python, or Ruby to create the website's backend. This includes the website's data storage, processing, and logic. Backend developers also work with APIs and databases to connect the website to other systems.

In short, frontend developers are responsible for making websites look good, while backend developers are responsible for making websites work. Both roles are essential for creating a successful website.
